Package com.distrimind.bouncycastle.voms

Class VOMSAttribute

java.lang.Object
com.distrimind.bouncycastle.voms.VOMSAttribute
public class VOMSAttribute extends Object
Representation of the authorization information (VO, server address and list of Fully Qualified Attribute Names, or FQANs) contained in a VOMS attribute certificate.
